# 🔹 Complexity Analysis

| Operation | Average | Worst |
| --------- | ------- | ----- |
| Search    | O(1)    | O(n)  |
| Insert    | O(1)    | O(n)  |
| Delete    | O(1)    | O(n)  |

---

# 🔹 Common GATE Traps

### Trap 1

Hashing gives O(1) average case.

NOT always O(1).

Worst case:

[
O(n)
]

---

### Trap 2

Load factor affects performance.

---

### Trap 3

Linear probing causes:

Primary clustering.

---

### Trap 4

Hash table is NOT sorted.

